6 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the task force may meet as often as necessary
7 and shall submit a written report of its findings, recommendations, and any proposed
8 legislation to the Senate Committee on Health and Welfare on or before February 1, 2027.
9 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the task force shall terminate on the date of
10 submission of its report or February 1, 2027, whichever occurs first.
11 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
12 secretary of the Louisiana Department of Health, the director of the Louisiana Tumor
13 Registry, and John M. Lyons, III, MD, State Chair for Louisiana Clinical Associate
14 Professor of Surgery, LSU Department of Surgery.
